%^BOLD%^%^BLUE%^Lawful Good %^WHITE%^- %^RED%^The Crusader
%^RESET%^Lawful good alignment combines honor and compassion. A character of this alignment acts as a good person is expected or required to act. She combines a commitment to oppose evil with the discipline to fight relentlessly. She tells the truth, keeps her word, helps those in need, and speaks out against injustice. A lawful good character hates to see the guilty go unpunished.